{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I kept telling Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mathis, ?] who is my neurosurgeon-- Jacob [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mathis ?] in San Francisco, a fine neurosurgeon, who operated me everywhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, doctor, it feels as though my bone is rubbing against bone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, oh, Gloria, if that were the case, you wouldn't be able to talk to me or you would be in such pain.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, doctor, that's what I'm trying to tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am in a lot of pain, and I can't lie down at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- it's excruciatingly painful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he finally realized what was happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't have all the equipment that we have today that one could really find out much easier as to what the problem is.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my seventh camp was at Ravensbruck and from there we were shipped out quite suddenly, as usual-- at night, in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that train moved for three days, just moved and stopped, moved and stopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently quite aimlessly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At long last, we arrived at an open meadow and there the-- we were kept locked in the cattle cars, and we heard the-- in German-- voices outside that here they're going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were all going to die, and we just couldn't believe that it would end like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "About 50%, at least 50%, of the women with me were dead, and we were sitting on them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And finally, they asked-- they-- they opened the doors and-- of the cattle car and said, push out the dead and the sick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we couldn't get ourselves to hurt the sick anymore, so we just-- if they're going to shoot us, let them.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
